\manualsummary{%
  A comprehensive reference manual for the OmniLaTeX document class.
  Covers every functionality of modern \LaTeX{} through 58 chapters:
  installation, 26 document types, typography, mathematics,
  internationalization (18 languages + CJK/RTL), figures, tables,
  TikZ diagrams, bibliographies, glossaries, code listings,
  presentations, posters, accessibility, and formal verification
  via Lean~4.
}

